t addicts \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E \u002BREP!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VR_Dev","CreatedById":92196,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-06T14:52:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EDude, thank you so much. I work super hard in my videos to be able to control everything without the UI up, but the camera setting when switching between crafts was the absolute worst.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThis is fantastic.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gaalidas","CreatedById":111158,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-06T15:32:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIngenious! More add-ons that we didn\u0027t even know we needed.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ZobrAA","CreatedById":65233,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-06T15:37:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EQuestion: plugin hides GUI text on F2 or on any other hotkey binded to HideGUI?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MrHappyFace","CreatedById":76365,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-06T18:37:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ZobrAA\u0022 data-cite=\u0022ZobrAA\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EQuestion: plugin hides GUI text on F2 or on any other hotkey binded to HideGUI?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt will hide screen messages when any key bound to Hide UI is pressed.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"One-Way Films","CreatedById":90926,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-06T21:16:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://community.us.playstation.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/257423i450CA8BFA1A9D844/image-size/original?v=mpbl-1\u0026amp;px=-1\u0022 alt=\u0022original?v=mpbl-1\u0026amp;px=-1\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E...that is all... thank you!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ZobrAA","CreatedById":65233,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-07T04:23:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuot